version_description:
Easily fulfill money requests (and more)!

Now family and friends can request money, mobile reloads, or bill payments using Xoom’s website. They enter their own information, so it’s more accurate and easier for you.

We relay the details to you. You can accept or decline requests with just a few taps.

- Get request notifications in the app
- See full request details
- Easily accept or decline requests
